1) Start up a CouchDB >= 1.1 instance.  If your OS doesn't support a package,
try the Couchbase preview releases:

    http://files.couchbase.com/developer-previews/couchbase-single-server-2.0.0-dev-preview/

2) Install Kanso

    http://kansojs.org/download.html

3) Unzip pages package.

4) Push the pages and admin apps to your couch:

    kanso push pages
    kanso pushadmin pages

5) Create pages with the built-in Kanso admin and make your site.
